The Factory Behind the Drug Nobody Can Get

Thesis
Peptide API manufacturing capacity is the structural constraint on GLP-1 supply — observable in primary CDMO investor filings at 0.80 corpus confidence — while originator names trade at peak-hype convergence and the manufacturing layer sits entirely outside option flow. The picks-and-shovels CDMO expression carries lower franchise-headline risk and has not been priced by the narrative wave that has taxed LLY and NVO.

